Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.55,0:00:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Connecting old words\Nthat have been used up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to convey\Nmy simple thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day's faint wind blows away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the castle ruins of yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll laugh with you\Nand live for the moment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still that incident\Nwill continue to trouble you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it must be good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.88,0:01:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving nothing behind,\Nlet us share what is left
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In time, we'll realize\Nthat it was everything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And sadness will touch our cheeks,\Ncreating a river of tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trembling thoughts swept into a vortex\Nand melting away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.59,0:02:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh! It’s over…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Losing is not an Option
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just barely…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…I was able to throw it off\Njust a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s now realized the secret\Nof the Byakugan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the meaning of this?\NHow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was he able to throw it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a whole six inches\Nfrom his vital point?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see… That Chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:03:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was emitting Chakra\Nthe whole time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and covered the area surrounding him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in a wide range to that extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder he was able\Nto detect the arrow and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,throw off the trajectory of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But constantly emitting that\Nmuch Chakra is a death throe…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn’t go that far,\Nhe can’t dodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, there’s no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s as I hypothesized…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The arrow earlier was\Ntotally invisible to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn’t carry out useless attacks…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And from the results,\Nhe accurately examines the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And…he’s also discovered\Nthe weakness of my eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the enemies\NI’ve fought until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this guy’s the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has 360-degree sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he unfailingly detects attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that penetrate the roughly\N150-feeot circumference around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there were Kunai Knives\Nhe couldn’t evade completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn’t he evade them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he couldn’t see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, even his Visual Jutsu\Nhas a slight blind spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being unable to see Kunai Knives\Nentering that blind spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he’s unable to react.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was dealing with attacks\Nfrom the blind spot
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with that defense technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I analyzed all the attacks\NI carried out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and grasped them perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right behind his first thoracic vertebra…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there exists a blind spot expanding\Nfrom a very small point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, if he moves and\Ndoesn’t stabilize the blind spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it becomes difficult to aim there\Nwith an arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But such a trick…doesn’t fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentle Fist is pointless if\Nyou don’t come close to your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can’t afford to think about\Napproaching me at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s about how to escape now…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though whether you struggle or not,\Nyou’re going to die anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh… It seems you only\Nhave a little Chakra left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fate of the small fry character\Nin an easy game
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is to be destroyed right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A thread?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, with this thread…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, the trajectory was thrown off\Nslightly by the trees, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that’s the case…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll add some rotation this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So even if it hits a tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it’ll just cut through and the trajectory\Nwon’t be thrown off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as before…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll control the arrow up until\N150 feet away from him
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,using a thread with Chakra\Nflowing through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll take aim at the moving target…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and plunge the arrow into\Nthe blind spot with a pinpoint attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s still standing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s strong…\NHe’s much stronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hardly have any Chakra left now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably won’t be able to evade\Nhis next attack completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll win no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto… I wonder what you’d do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t dodge it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s stopped moving…\NHas he given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just to make doubly sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maximum destructive power\Nwith 120% accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentle Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? He still…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! My attack just now\Nshould’ve made the kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Substance with Chakra base…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s meaningless against Gentle Fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentle Fist…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, in his final moments,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he funneled the last Chakra\Nthrough the thread!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight crows…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again I couldn’t see one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:10:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He damaged several of\Nmy internal organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…I can still move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You failure…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you… I don’t know when to quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you try to go against\Nyour destiny that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was called…a failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you’re going to say it’s futile,\Nyou don’t have to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I become the Hokage,\NI’ll change Hyuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ninjutsu that you’re good at, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was careless…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clone Jutsu was the Ninjutsu\NI stunk at.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be whining about boring stuff\Nlike destiny and what not,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and how it can’t be changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're not a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it’s become the three of us…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry about such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Choji and Neji will\Ncatch up right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choji had the trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I’ve fought Neji\Nin the Chunin exam, so I know…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That he’s…a true genius. Believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot lose…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether he’s an enemy\Nmuch stronger than me…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or even if this body should fail me…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a reason why I cannot lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve had a hard time of it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I played too long…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t build up Chakra…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How? You should’ve\Nbeen instantly killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come you’re alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn’t completely\Nevade it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was prepared to deliberately\Ntake the hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I knew of my own weakness\Nmuch more than you do…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were eight crows, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Byakugan has a blind spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if I knew that your attack\Nwould only come from there…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could release my Chakra just\Nto that blind spot and detect the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not so difficult to make
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a move of just a few inches\Nto throw off the aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’d suffer a serious injury,\Nbut instant death can be avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.34,0:14:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you took the hit deliberately…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn’t change the fact\Nthat you’re going to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you go that far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Of all the enemies,”\Nyou’re the strongest I’ve ever fought…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there’s a reason why I cannot lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all those I’ve ever fought,\Nthe strongest one said this to me…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Unlike me…you are not a failure!\N– Unlike me…you are not a failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve been called a genius all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I cannot lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for the sake of those guys\Nwho believe
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that this humdrum and small me\Nis a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“The fate of the small fry character\Nin a game is to be destroyed right away.”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things like fate,\Nisn’t determined by someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also look like\Nyou’re going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neji, live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than anyone in the clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you’re the man loved most\Nby the Hyuga ability…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot die so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you act tough,\Nyou can’t stem the current now…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Sasuke ran to\Nthe Sound Village by his own wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke is now in the darkness…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto… You’ve got better eyes than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s a person who can find him\Nin the darkness and save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.79,0:17:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Sasuke belongs\Nto Lord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who it may be,\Nthey can’t save…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because…Naruto…you…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me from the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking rubbish until the end…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven’t been pushed this far\Nsince Kimimaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you think it was\Na bother if I approached you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite my doubts,\NI worked up my courage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My clumsy attempts with words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.17,0:21:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You listened without turning away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder I get carried away by you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don’t feel anything for me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.59,0:22:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so sad
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.79,0:22:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.55,0:22:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.00,0:22:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.25,0:22:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo! The enemies are quite close!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:22:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! We’ll catch up in a burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:22:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking in terms of number,\Nwe’ve got more!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.05,0:23:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If things go well,\Nwe can get him back next!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.79,0:23:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I don’t feel like losing\Nwith four against two!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.79,0:23:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four against two?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s twice the opponents’ number!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.79,0:23:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say-say. Were there four of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.25,0:23:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?!\NMe, Akamaru, Shikamaru, and you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.17,0:23:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you count,\Nthere are four!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode:\N“The Vessel Arrives Too Late”
